页面，没有修复，是百度不够重视吗？好那下面就看我如何一步一步放大危害。<br>参考 http://wooyun.org/bugs/wooyun-2014-072520 ，将QQ昵称改为如下代码后，在百度网盘登录并分享文件，</p>\n\n<fieldset class=\"fieldset fieldset-code\"><pre><code>\";};alert(1)//</code></pre></fieldset>\n\n<p class=\"detail\"> 得到链接 http://pan.baidu.com/s/1kTqTrzL 。<br>将浏览器UA修改为手机后，访问该链接会返回手机版页面，同时触发我们注入的JS代码。<br></p>\n\n<p class=\"detail usemasaic\"><a href=\"http://showmethemoney.hnengdata.com/image_security/10-16/201409/30193014b159a3c574ff11d33cf3f5742e215854.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://showmethemoney.hnengdata.com/image_security/10-16/201409/30193014b159a3c574ff11d33cf3f5742e215854.png\" alt=\"sshot-2014-09-30-[1].png\" width=\"600\" onerror=\"javascript:errimg(this);\"></a></p>\n\n<p class=\"detail\"><br>是否存在一打开就是WAP版的链接呢? 我们百度一下 pan,baidu.com wap 看看:<br></p>\n\n<p class=\"detail usemasaic\"><a href=\"http://showmethemoney.hnengdata.com/image_security/10-16/201409/30193337be593d47f8f93c777249981e5250edc5.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://showmethemoney.hnengdata.com/image_security/10-16/201409/30193337be593d47f8f93c777249981e5250edc5.png\" alt=\"sshot-2014-09-30-[2].png\" width=\"600\" onerror=\"javascript:errimg(this);\"></a></p>\n\n<p class=\"detail\"><br>这条链接打开就是WAP版的下载页，看来有戏了:</p>\n\n<p class=\"detail usemasaic\"><a href=\"http://showmethemoney.hnengdata.com/image_security/10-16/201409/301934246bd3429273059c72e4504df43ab0816c.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://showmethemoney.hnengdata.com/image_security/10-16/201409/301934246bd3429273059c72e4504df43ab0816c.png\" alt=\"sshot-2014-09-30-[3].png\" width=\"600\" onerror=\"javascript:errimg(this);\"></a></p>\n\n<p class=\"detail\"><br>把链接中的uk与shareid参数修改为 http://pan.baidu.com/s/1kTqTrzL 对应的值，这两个参数在页面源码中都可以找到</p>\n\n<p class=\"detail usemasaic\"><a href=\"http://showmethemoney.hnengdata.com/image_security/10-16/201409/301936172804b58ef5fec5c966d841706787792c.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://showmethemoney.hnengdata.com/image_security/10-16/201409/301936172804b58ef5f