age_security/10-16/201408/16085936bcac2f08d484de50f2e3304aadb88ff9.png\" alt=\"2.PNG\" width=\"600\" onerror=\"javascript:errimg(this);\"></a></p>\n\n<p class=\"detail\"><br>2、输入两遍新密码：1qaz@WSX （其余信息任意填写），发送并抓包<br></p>\n\n<p class=\"detail usemasaic\"><a href=\"http://showmethemoney.hnengdata.com/image_security/10-16/201408/16090040ad6dd774c388bd04c1114eb070967466.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://showmethemoney.hnengdata.com/image_security/10-16/201408/16090040ad6dd774c388bd04c1114eb070967466.png\" alt=\"3.PNG\" width=\"600\" onerror=\"javascript:errimg(this);\"></a></p>\n\n<p class=\"detail\"><br>更改user_id参数，由144更改为140和145<br></p>\n\n<p class=\"detail usemasaic\"><a href=\"http://showmethemoney.hnengdata.com/image_security/10-16/201408/1609014611ba042b3478b2003a9b05e02b249d6c.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://showmethemoney.hnengdata.com/image_security/10-16/201408/1609014611ba042b3478b2003a9b05e02b249d6c.png\" alt=\"4.PNG\" width=\"600\" onerror=\"javascript:errimg(this);\"></a></p>\n\n<p class=\"detail\"><br></p>\n\n<p class=\"detail usemasaic\"><a href=\"http://showmethemoney.hnengdata.com/image_security/10-16/201408/1609020715a9031144c82f89f0cefaab37dd86d8.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://showmethemoney.hnengdata.com/image_security/10-16/201408/1609020715a9031144c82f89f0cefaab37dd86d8.png\" alt=\"5.PNG\" width=\"600\" onerror=\"javascript:errimg(this);\"></a></p>\n\n<p class=\"detail\"><br> </p>    </div>									<h3 class=\"detailTitle\">漏洞证明：</h3>      <div class=\"wybug_poc\">			<p class=\"detail\">3、退出堡垒机后，使用密码1qaz@WSX登陆liu***和cha***账号，显示登陆成功，<br></p>\n\n<p class=\"detail usemasaic\"><a href=\"http://showmethemoney.hnengdata.com/image_security/10-16/201408/160902474f067ab3c4902e1344100593f6441d7f.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://showmethemoney.hnengdata.com/image_security/10-16/201408/160902474f067ab3c4902e1344100593f6441d7f.png\" alt=\"6.PNG\" width=\"600\" onerror=\"javascript:errimg(this);\"></a></p>\n\n<p class=\"detail